Notes for solaris libs:

Host system: x86 Solaris Express(12-06)

JPEG:
version: 6b

PNG:
version: 1.2.16
notes: LDFLAGS and CPPFLAGS were changed to point to prefix directory where custom zlib was installed. --disable-shared was given as configure option.

FLTK:
notes: LDFLAGS and CPPFLAGS set to point to custom compiled versions of zlib, png and jpeg. CXXFLAGS set to -fexceptions for exception support.
version: 1.1.7

ZLIB:
version: 1.2.3

NCURSES:
configure command: ./configure --with-terminfo-dirs=/usr/share/lib/terminfo/
version: 5.6
notes: Colors don't work on xterms

X (libX11, libXext)
notes: used from basesystem

GCC (libstdc++, libutil)
version: 3.4.3
notes: used from basesystem

LUA:
version 5.1.1
make command: make posix
notes: src/Makefile was edited to use g++ instead of gcc (enables C++ exception support, important) and to use the -Os CFLAG.
